    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Draft Your Deck of Gemblades!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gemblades is a single-player deckbuilder where you draft a deck of powerful heroes called Gemblades </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and battle against the forces of Onyxion, the Dragon Lord.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165590/extras/2be5e41fd53e92805c2d57e102c0a69b.poster.avif?t=1769446128\" width=700 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165590/extras/2be5e41fd53e92805c2d57e102c0a69b.webm?t=1769446128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165590/extras/2be5e41fd53e92805c2d57e102c0a69b.mp4?t=1769446128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each Gemtype has their own identity!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every Gemblade is empowered by the magical properties of their own Gemtype. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Emerald: Growth and balance in everything.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ruby: First on the battlefield and selfless to a fault.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sapphire:  Seekers of knowledge, legendary tacticians. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165590/extras/ee821f78d1d2befe65d759e382faddfa.poster.avif?t=1769446128\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165590/extras/ee821f78d1d2befe65d759e382faddfa.webm?t=1769446128\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165590/extras/ee821f78d1d2befe65d759e382faddfa.mp4?t=1769446128\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Show your skill on the Global Leaderboards!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire Gemblades and combine their power to defeat the minions of Onyxion to save the world from his invasion!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's also a Global Leaderboard where you can compete with others in the multiverse of Gemblades!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our Discord to stay up to date with announcements and learn about future tournaments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See you there, Gemblade!</p>",
